BAN (death)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get banned over and over again, reincarnate, and become the King of Streamers!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097780/extras/42d75f7a70982844d55e6a0bb516be51.avif?t=1733976912\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097780/extras_big/42d75f7a70982844d55e6a0bb516be51.avif?t=1733976912 width=800 height=268 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Your Goal</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve 100 million fans</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat Top Streamers<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097780/extras/bda8ab4a635ad7a65ff8d2a1cef5fad5.avif?t=1733976912\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097780/extras_big/bda8ab4a635ad7a65ff8d2a1cef5fad5.avif?t=1733976912 width=800 height=298 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Battle System</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy battles with <strong>Auto Battle</strong>!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097780/extras/98a6e24c8a5829786cf427b81fa3d004.poster.avif?t=1733976912\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097780/extras/98a6e24c8a5829786cf427b81fa3d004.webm?t=1733976912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097780/extras/98a6e24c8a5829786cf427b81fa3d004.mp4?t=1733976912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p 