 content for your streams!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note) This game does not have an online multiplayer function.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Streaming is allowed without permission for both individuals and organizations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Monetization is only permitted if using the features provided by the video streaming platform.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・We would appreciate it if you could include the game's name in the video or stream title, or add a link to the Steam page in the description.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, we take no responsibility for any damages caused by streaming videos of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These guidelines are subject to change without prior notice.</p>",
